beer_brewer_name: Crispin Cider Company (Tenth and Blake Beer Co. - MillerCoors)
review_blob: Hands down best cider Ive ever had. Whats not to love great flavor great color and out of bounds taste and a smooth silky mouth feel. Best crispin product ever made.

beer_brewer_name: Crispin Cider Company (Tenth and Blake Beer Co. - MillerCoors)
review_blob: Love this cider. Great taste even better nose. Its even enjoyable to look at. Being unfiltered gives it a great mouth feel unlike most ciders.
